          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total photoabsorption cross sections for He-4 has",
                " been measured for the first time over a  wide photon",
                " energy range from 200 to 800 MeV. By using the large",
                " acceptance  detector  DAPHNE  at  the  tagged photon",
                " facility of MAMI accelerator in Mainz high precision",
                " results with small systematic errors were obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
